  grfcodec-9999.ebuild:
  Add blocker on nforenum, since it is included now.

  12 Feb 2011; Locke Shinseiko <wizzleby@gmail.com> -grfcodec-1.0.0.ebuild,
  grfcodec-5.1.0.ebuild, grfcodec-9999.ebuild:
